1
00:01:58,640 --> 00:02:01,230
This wound was inflicted by Liu Chu.

2
00:02:01,950 --> 00:02:03,480
If I don't destroy Jinglan,

3
00:02:03,680 --> 00:02:05,740
then I am not worthy to be called a man.

4
00:02:07,640 --> 00:02:08,570
You must help me.

5
00:02:09,910 --> 00:02:11,840
Help me wipe out this humiliation.

6
00:02:12,310 --> 00:02:13,680
Rest assured, Your Majesty.

7
00:02:13,680 --> 00:02:15,000
I will do my best.

8
00:02:15,960 --> 00:02:18,280
If we cannot secure
a swift victory on the battlefield,

9
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:20,540
then we will tear them apart from within.

10
00:02:26,680 --> 00:02:27,470
Good.

11
00:02:28,240 --> 00:02:29,030
Good.

12
00:02:30,520 --> 00:02:31,430
Oh.

13
00:02:31,560 --> 00:02:32,890
You've done much for me.

14
00:02:33,750 --> 00:02:34,560
Rest assured.

15
00:02:35,680 --> 00:02:37,310
When Jinglan falls,

16
00:02:37,560 --> 00:02:38,360
that will be

17
00:02:38,680 --> 00:02:40,710
the day I name you my queen.

18
00:02:44,680 --> 00:02:46,750
As long as I can stay by your side,

19
00:02:48,120 --> 00:02:49,750
I will be content.

20
00:02:50,079 --> 00:02:51,240
Father.

21
00:02:54,520 --> 00:02:55,680
Lord Meng.

22
00:02:56,910 --> 00:02:58,520
I have other matters to handle.

23
00:02:58,520 --> 00:02:59,910
Stay here and keep your father company.

24
00:02:59,910 --> 00:03:00,750
Okay.

25
00:03:01,520 --> 00:03:02,520
Greetings, Fa...

26
00:03:04,360 --> 00:03:05,620
Father, your wound...

27
00:03:06,120 --> 00:03:06,870
What?

28
00:03:07,800 --> 00:03:09,150
Is this how you bow to me?

29
00:03:09,710 --> 00:03:12,370
Is that what
the ceremonial officer taught you?

30
00:03:14,960 --> 00:03:16,150
Greetings, Father.

31
00:03:16,400 --> 00:03:17,000
Hmm.

32
00:03:17,430 --> 00:03:18,560
That's more like it.

33
00:03:23,520 --> 00:03:24,280
Father.

34
00:03:24,630 --> 00:03:26,150
Since I was a child, you had me taught

35
00:03:26,150 --> 00:03:27,030
virtue, humility,

36
00:03:27,030 --> 00:03:28,240
and all the rules of court etiquette.

37
00:03:28,240 --> 00:03:29,910
But what use are any of those?

38
00:03:30,030 --> 00:03:31,710
In Changmo, besides you,

39
00:03:31,710 --> 00:03:34,110
who else deserves
such a formal bow from me?

40
00:03:34,360 --> 00:03:36,520
Even if you do not bow to me,

41
00:03:37,079 --> 00:03:39,910
you must bow
to your husband in the future.

42
00:03:39,910 --> 00:03:41,000
Liu Chu?

43
00:03:41,120 --> 00:03:41,630
Yes.

44
00:03:43,520 --> 00:03:45,030
Ever since I was young,
you've told me that

45
00:03:45,030 --> 00:03:46,750
one day I would marry

46
00:03:46,750 --> 00:03:48,560
Liu Chu, the prince of Jinglan.

47
00:03:49,310 --> 00:03:50,840
But I've never even met him.

48
00:03:51,150 --> 00:03:53,960
Even though you've never met,

49
00:03:54,360 --> 00:03:57,030
he already loves you deeply.

50
00:03:57,190 --> 00:03:58,120
He loves me?

51
00:03:58,910 --> 00:04:00,240
How much does he love me?

52
00:04:00,360 --> 00:04:02,150
Well, let me put it this way.

53
00:04:03,080 --> 00:04:04,910
He is your destined one.

54
00:04:05,560 --> 00:04:06,840
In the near future,

55
00:04:06,870 --> 00:04:09,730
he will bring you back
to Jinglan in a grand wedding,

56
00:04:10,030 --> 00:04:12,160
and make you his most beloved consort.

57
00:04:12,470 --> 00:04:14,120
You will have many children,

58
00:04:14,520 --> 00:04:16,630
and spend your life in happiness

59
00:04:16,680 --> 00:04:18,279
within his splendid palace.

60
00:04:18,720 --> 00:04:20,430
Who would want to have children with him?

61
00:04:20,430 --> 00:04:22,480
I want to stay with you forever.

62
00:04:24,600 --> 00:04:25,950
You silly girl.

63
00:04:26,480 --> 00:04:27,720
By then,

64
00:04:27,750 --> 00:04:30,950
Jinglan and Changmo will be one family.

65
00:04:31,160 --> 00:04:34,510
We can invite Liu Chu to Changmo.

66
00:04:34,750 --> 00:04:35,800
That way,

67
00:04:35,800 --> 00:04:37,130
you can stay with Liu Chu

68
00:04:37,310 --> 00:04:38,720
and also stay with me.

69
00:04:39,270 --> 00:04:40,070
How about that?

70
00:04:40,070 --> 00:04:40,680
Good.

71
00:04:46,070 --> 00:04:47,360
Thank you, Father.

72
00:04:48,310 --> 00:04:49,360
I believe

73
00:04:49,360 --> 00:04:51,390
Liu Chu and I will be happy together.

74
00:04:51,830 --> 00:04:53,480
I also hope there will never be war

75
00:04:53,480 --> 00:04:55,310
between our two nations again.

76
00:05:05,240 --> 00:05:06,040
Princess.

77
00:05:06,070 --> 00:05:07,830
Lord Fei, General Xiao.

78
00:05:08,270 --> 00:05:09,510
Princess, you haven't
entered the palace yet,

79
00:05:09,510 --> 00:05:11,510
so the daily greetings
are still necessary.

80
00:05:11,510 --> 00:05:12,510
What greetings?

81
00:05:12,950 --> 00:05:14,350
It's just surveillance.

82
00:05:14,430 --> 00:05:15,950
The princess holds a noble status.

83
00:05:15,950 --> 00:05:18,040
We just want to ensure her safety.

84
00:05:18,680 --> 00:05:20,240
Lord Fei, thank you.

85
00:05:20,920 --> 00:05:21,360
It's nothing.

86
00:05:21,360 --> 00:05:23,560
So you know we are here
for a marriage alliance.

87
00:05:23,560 --> 00:05:24,750
Then when will your Emperor come

88
00:05:24,750 --> 00:05:26,210
to take the princess back?

89
00:05:26,430 --> 00:05:28,360
A marriage alliance is a matter
of great importance.

90
00:05:28,360 --> 00:05:29,510
It is complex and requires
careful preparation.

91
00:05:29,510 --> 00:05:31,310
Everything must be properly arranged.

92
00:05:31,310 --> 00:05:31,950
Princess,

93
00:05:32,159 --> 00:05:32,830
please believe that His Majesty

94
00:05:32,830 --> 00:05:35,360
will prepare a grand ceremony for you.

95
00:05:37,360 --> 00:05:39,480
Jin Xi, since we've arrived
in the capital,

96
00:05:39,480 --> 00:05:40,750
there's no need to rush.

97
00:05:40,750 --> 00:05:43,409
I believe His Majesty
has his own arrangements.

98
00:05:43,510 --> 00:05:44,950
We shall follow General Xiao's lead.

99
00:05:44,950 --> 00:05:46,560
Thank you for
your understanding, Princess.

100
00:05:46,560 --> 00:05:48,560
Then I will take my leave first.

101
00:05:54,630 --> 00:05:56,230
If you feel bored, Princess,

102
00:05:56,240 --> 00:05:58,240
you are free to walk around the courtyard.

103
00:05:58,240 --> 00:05:59,440
If you need anything,

104
00:05:59,510 --> 00:06:00,950
you can also ask General Chengfeng

105
00:06:00,950 --> 00:06:01,880
to buy it for you.

106
00:06:01,950 --> 00:06:02,480
All right.

107
00:06:02,480 --> 00:06:03,000
Then,

108
00:06:03,310 --> 00:06:05,240
I will take my leave as well.

109
00:06:14,430 --> 00:06:16,560
Jin Xi, don't worry.

110
00:06:16,830 --> 00:06:18,160
I trust Father's words.

111
00:06:18,720 --> 00:06:19,920
Liu Chu will surely be

112
00:06:20,310 --> 00:06:22,560
a husband who loves me deeply.

113
00:06:26,240 --> 00:06:27,240
This wine is good.

114
00:06:27,830 --> 00:06:28,630
Have a taste.

115
00:06:30,360 --> 00:06:31,560
I still have official matters
to attend to later,

116
00:06:31,560 --> 00:06:32,560
so I won't drink.

117
00:06:34,310 --> 00:06:35,360
You and Xiao Chi—

118
00:06:35,750 --> 00:06:36,950
one refuses to drink,

119
00:06:37,360 --> 00:06:39,420
the other doesn't even show up at all.

120
00:06:39,560 --> 00:06:41,560
Your Majesty,
you suddenly have the mood for drinking—

121
00:06:41,560 --> 00:06:43,220
has something good happened?

122
00:06:43,720 --> 00:06:44,600
Yesterday,

123
00:06:44,870 --> 00:06:47,680
Lord Li brought Wang Ruhai
to me to plead for mercy.

124
00:06:47,680 --> 00:06:48,480
I refused.

125
00:06:48,560 --> 00:06:49,510
Is that so?

126
00:06:49,920 --> 00:06:51,560
You should have seen it.

127
00:06:51,750 --> 00:06:53,000
He knelt under the blazing sun

128
00:06:53,000 --> 00:06:54,430
for two whole hours.

129
00:06:54,510 --> 00:06:56,430
He was limping when he got up to leave.

130
00:06:56,430 --> 00:06:57,830
It was quite satisfying.

131
00:06:59,360 --> 00:07:00,190
Well.

132
00:07:00,630 --> 00:07:02,430
Wang Ruhai got what he deserved.

133
00:07:02,950 --> 00:07:05,480
What a pity I didn't get to
see his sorry state.

134
00:07:05,680 --> 00:07:06,430
Ah.

135
00:07:07,390 --> 00:07:08,160
Ah.

136
00:07:08,430 --> 00:07:09,190
Damn it.

137
00:07:09,510 --> 00:07:09,950
I...

138
00:07:10,680 --> 00:07:11,120
I...

139
00:07:11,560 --> 00:07:12,360
I'm really...

140
00:07:14,360 --> 00:07:16,360
furious.

141
00:07:18,720 --> 00:07:20,430
His Majesty.

142
00:07:21,310 --> 00:07:21,830
Humph.

143
00:07:22,270 --> 00:07:22,870
No.

144
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:26,360
Liu Chu, Xiao Chi and Fei Zheng,

145
00:07:26,680 --> 00:07:28,360
just you wait.

146
00:07:28,920 --> 00:07:30,270
All of you—

147
00:07:30,430 --> 00:07:31,560
just wait!

148
00:07:32,120 --> 00:07:32,950
By the way,

149
00:07:33,950 --> 00:07:35,159
when do you plan

150
00:07:35,630 --> 00:07:37,960
to set the date for the marriage alliance?

151
00:07:38,680 --> 00:07:41,120
We can take our time with this.

152
00:07:41,120 --> 00:07:42,510
I'm not in a hurry anyway.

153
00:07:42,510 --> 00:07:44,560
Aren't you curious

154
00:07:44,560 --> 00:07:46,620
what the Princess of Changmo is like?

155
00:07:46,830 --> 00:07:48,310
If

156
00:07:48,920 --> 00:07:51,720
I see an ugly woman

157
00:07:52,430 --> 00:07:53,890
at the marriage ceremony,

158
00:07:53,950 --> 00:07:54,950
can I back out?

159
00:07:56,560 --> 00:07:57,950
Of course you can't.

160
00:07:58,920 --> 00:07:59,870
So, Your Majesty...

161
00:07:59,870 --> 00:08:01,680
don't you want to

162
00:08:01,750 --> 00:08:03,750
see her yourself?

163
00:08:04,630 --> 00:08:06,830
You really know how to keep me guessing.

164
00:08:08,120 --> 00:08:09,680
But I'm not falling for it.

165
00:08:09,950 --> 00:08:11,070
Well.

166
00:08:11,070 --> 00:08:12,830
This pond is nice,

167
00:08:12,830 --> 00:08:14,830
yet no fish can be caught here.

168
00:08:15,160 --> 00:08:17,560
Yes. I am

169
00:08:17,920 --> 00:08:19,380
like the fish in this pond.

170
00:08:20,830 --> 00:08:23,750
I look quite free when I'm inside,

171
00:08:24,480 --> 00:08:26,360
but it's not so easy to get out.

172
00:08:27,830 --> 00:08:30,240
I really miss the time we spent

173
00:08:30,360 --> 00:08:31,920
in the manor as children.

174
00:08:33,630 --> 00:08:35,240
I always dream about it.

175
00:08:36,960 --> 00:08:38,120
To be honest, Your Majesty,

176
00:08:38,120 --> 00:08:40,549
I actually dream about it often too.

177
00:08:41,630 --> 00:08:42,440
Oh, right.

178
00:08:42,549 --> 00:08:44,510
Recently I've moved
into the Xiao residence

179
00:08:44,510 --> 00:08:45,710
to live with Xiao Chi.

180
00:08:46,750 --> 00:08:48,870
So that means I'm the only one here?

181
00:08:50,080 --> 00:08:51,870
Seems so.

182
00:08:53,910 --> 00:08:54,630
Got one!

183
00:08:55,960 --> 00:08:56,720
Wow!

184
00:08:57,440 --> 00:08:58,670
Congratulations, Your Majesty.

185
00:08:58,670 --> 00:09:01,550
I will have a few drinks
with Xiao Chi tonight

186
00:09:01,550 --> 00:09:03,480
to celebrate your lucky catch.

187
00:09:04,270 --> 00:09:06,670
Maybe I should find a way these days

188
00:09:06,910 --> 00:09:08,630
to sneak out of the palace

189
00:09:08,630 --> 00:09:09,890
and come to your place.

190
00:09:09,960 --> 00:09:11,600
I'll sneak back

191
00:09:11,600 --> 00:09:13,060
before the morning court.

192
00:09:13,360 --> 00:09:14,490
Is that really okay?

193
00:09:14,720 --> 00:09:16,050
What's wrong with that?

194
00:09:16,120 --> 00:09:16,920
It's settled.

195
00:09:17,320 --> 00:09:20,240
Then, I obey your command.

196
00:09:21,320 --> 00:09:22,720
Let's catch another one.

197
00:09:22,870 --> 00:09:24,510
Since we're looking for good wine,

198
00:09:24,510 --> 00:09:26,750
I believe Ms. Tang must have some here.

199
00:09:27,120 --> 00:09:29,150
Xiao Chi, you're finally here.

200
00:09:29,150 --> 00:09:31,030
Good wine always reminds me of you.

201
00:09:31,030 --> 00:09:32,600
Then you've come to the right place.

202
00:09:32,600 --> 00:09:33,120
Please.

203
00:09:37,630 --> 00:09:40,510
The finest wine
from Tianlang Pass is here.

204
00:09:40,510 --> 00:09:41,910
This is...

205
00:09:42,720 --> 00:09:44,630
This is my father.

206
00:09:44,910 --> 00:09:46,240
I'm also the owner here.

207
00:09:47,150 --> 00:09:48,630
You are indeed capable.

208
00:09:48,630 --> 00:09:50,320
You've already
brought in guests so quickly.

209
00:09:50,320 --> 00:09:52,480
They're friends who came to support us.

210
00:09:52,480 --> 00:09:54,480
This is Xiao Chi.

211
00:09:54,480 --> 00:09:55,510
General Xiao?

212
00:09:55,510 --> 00:09:56,960
Aren't you meant to
be guarding Tianlang Pass?

213
00:09:56,960 --> 00:09:58,620
Why are you in the capital too?

214
00:09:59,240 --> 00:10:01,270
If he didn't come,
I wouldn't have come either.

215
00:10:01,270 --> 00:10:02,390
Pour the wine.

216
00:10:02,390 --> 00:10:03,360
Okay.

217
00:10:06,960 --> 00:10:07,750
Thank you.

218
00:10:18,960 --> 00:10:19,790
How is it?

219
00:10:19,960 --> 00:10:22,080
This wine is indeed good,

220
00:10:22,480 --> 00:10:23,940
but still not quite there.

221
00:10:24,360 --> 00:10:26,360
Is this the finest wine we have here?

222
00:10:26,440 --> 00:10:27,840
Yes, definitely.

223
00:10:28,600 --> 00:10:29,200
It's fine.

224
00:10:29,240 --> 00:10:30,960
Ms. Tang, we will

225
00:10:30,960 --> 00:10:32,000
try other places in the capital.

226
00:10:32,000 --> 00:10:32,480
Wait.

227
00:10:34,910 --> 00:10:36,150
Hurry

228
00:10:36,870 --> 00:10:40,480
and bring us another jar of our best wine.

229
00:10:40,750 --> 00:10:42,320
Good wine?

230
00:10:43,080 --> 00:10:44,870
I do have one,

231
00:10:44,910 --> 00:10:46,550
but the price…

232
00:10:46,550 --> 00:10:47,870
it's priceless.

233
00:10:47,870 --> 00:10:49,240
Forget the price.

234
00:10:49,240 --> 00:10:50,240
Just bring it out.

235
00:10:51,150 --> 00:10:52,630
Hurry up.

236
00:10:52,960 --> 00:10:54,510
Alright, okay.

237
00:11:01,720 --> 00:11:03,000
He really is my father.

238
00:11:03,870 --> 00:11:04,910
Really.

239
00:11:06,720 --> 00:11:07,510
Well.

240
00:11:08,030 --> 00:11:10,030
This is top-quality Nverhong wine.

241
00:11:10,080 --> 00:11:12,270
I sealed it myself when you were born.

242
00:11:12,320 --> 00:11:13,750
I was planning to serve it to your groom

243
00:11:13,750 --> 00:11:14,840
on your wedding day.

244
00:11:14,840 --> 00:11:16,200
How come I've never heard

245
00:11:16,200 --> 00:11:17,550
that I even had it?

246
00:11:17,550 --> 00:11:18,910
Isn't Nverhong wine

247
00:11:18,910 --> 00:11:20,630
supposed to be buried
underground for years?

248
00:11:20,630 --> 00:11:21,960
You know quite a bit.

249
00:11:22,030 --> 00:11:25,030
I've carried it with me
all over the country for so many years.

250
00:11:25,030 --> 00:11:27,360
Wherever I went, I buried it in the soil.

251
00:11:27,360 --> 00:11:28,080
This wine

252
00:11:28,080 --> 00:11:29,030
has absorbed

253
00:11:29,030 --> 00:11:30,840
the essence of sun and moon
from all over Jinglan.

254
00:11:30,840 --> 00:11:32,240
I was even saving it for your husband

255
00:11:32,240 --> 00:11:33,630
on your wedding day.

256
00:11:33,720 --> 00:11:36,080
Who cares about all that?

257
00:11:36,320 --> 00:11:37,450
Don't listen to him.

258
00:11:37,550 --> 00:11:38,720
If you want to drink,

259
00:11:38,720 --> 00:11:39,840
just drink.

260
00:11:40,910 --> 00:11:41,510
Forget it.

261
00:11:41,510 --> 00:11:43,550
We really can't accept
such a generous gift.

262
00:11:43,550 --> 00:11:44,440
Besides,

263
00:11:44,440 --> 00:11:45,600
this wine is also a gift for someone.

264
00:11:45,600 --> 00:11:46,480
So what?

265
00:11:46,840 --> 00:11:49,440
Whoever it is that
made you go to such lengths

266
00:11:49,440 --> 00:11:50,770
must be extraordinary.

267
00:11:51,480 --> 00:11:53,320
If you really feel bad about it,

268
00:11:53,440 --> 00:11:55,750
I can deliver the wine for you.

269
00:11:56,440 --> 00:11:57,240
Well.

270
00:12:02,510 --> 00:12:04,510
Thank you, Ms. Tang.

271
00:12:16,480 --> 00:12:18,720
This place is quite unique.

272
00:12:19,360 --> 00:12:21,560
What kind of person are we going to meet?

273
00:12:21,870 --> 00:12:22,720
He's…

274
00:12:22,910 --> 00:12:24,030
a strange man.

275
00:12:24,030 --> 00:12:24,960
a strange man?

276
00:12:27,120 --> 00:12:28,360
Interesting.

277
00:12:49,360 --> 00:12:50,480
Good wine.

278
00:12:50,480 --> 00:12:52,120
Shiba, do you smell that?

279
00:12:55,030 --> 00:12:55,750
Where is the good wine?

280
00:12:55,750 --> 00:12:56,600
Where is it?

281
00:12:56,600 --> 00:12:57,360
Right here.

282
00:12:59,320 --> 00:13:00,150
Who are you?

283
00:13:00,960 --> 00:13:01,890
Doesn't matter.

284
00:13:02,270 --> 00:13:03,840
This wine is for me, right?

285
00:13:04,360 --> 00:13:05,550
Your brother's been well taken care of.

286
00:13:05,550 --> 00:13:07,010
Go in and see for yourself.

287
00:13:10,550 --> 00:13:12,510
You're something else—

288
00:13:12,510 --> 00:13:14,170
you even found such fine wine.

289
00:13:14,440 --> 00:13:15,370
Let me have a sip.

290
00:13:16,550 --> 00:13:18,150
Why are you so rude?

291
00:13:18,150 --> 00:13:20,270
I've brought the wine for you.

292
00:13:20,270 --> 00:13:21,510
Whether you get to drink it or not

293
00:13:21,510 --> 00:13:23,080
depends on your own ability.

294
00:13:23,080 --> 00:13:23,540
This...

295
00:13:26,510 --> 00:13:27,170
Ah, this...

296
00:13:27,960 --> 00:13:30,160
Tell me—how can I get to drink this wine?

297
00:13:31,630 --> 00:13:32,480
Alright then.

298
00:13:33,030 --> 00:13:35,360
If you can guess my age,

299
00:13:35,630 --> 00:13:37,910
this wine is yours.

300
00:13:37,910 --> 00:13:39,670
Why don't you just tell me?

301
00:13:40,120 --> 00:13:41,180
Not going to guess?

302
00:13:41,550 --> 00:13:43,840
Looks like you won't get to taste it then.

303
00:13:46,910 --> 00:13:48,630
You are twenty-four.

304
00:13:49,910 --> 00:13:50,840
How did you know?

305
00:13:50,870 --> 00:13:51,720
Curious?

306
00:13:52,000 --> 00:13:52,480
Yeah.

307
00:13:55,840 --> 00:13:56,630
Here.

308
00:14:02,270 --> 00:14:03,440
You can tell me now.

309
00:14:06,910 --> 00:14:09,320
In Jinglan, if a woman
isn't married by eighteen,

310
00:14:09,320 --> 00:14:10,550
she wears a hairpin.

311
00:14:11,150 --> 00:14:12,360
Each year, she wears
a different colored hairpin—

312
00:14:12,360 --> 00:14:13,960
red, orange, yellow,
green, blue, indigo, violet.

313
00:14:13,960 --> 00:14:15,890
Today you're wearing a violet one,

314
00:14:15,960 --> 00:14:17,550
so you must be twenty-four.

315
00:14:17,870 --> 00:14:18,960
Already twenty-four and still not married.

316
00:14:18,960 --> 00:14:19,480
You...

317
00:14:19,960 --> 00:14:21,360
Don't tell me she's planning to marry you?

318
00:14:21,360 --> 00:14:22,080
Let me tell you,

319
00:14:22,080 --> 00:14:23,120
the girl inside is a good one.

320
00:14:23,120 --> 00:14:24,380
Don't disappoint her.

321
00:14:24,510 --> 00:14:26,440
Liu Xiyang, just drink your wine.

322
00:14:29,510 --> 00:14:30,960
Little puppy,

323
00:14:31,150 --> 00:14:32,510
you are so cute.

324
00:14:32,600 --> 00:14:33,670
What's your name?

325
00:14:34,150 --> 00:14:36,550
Shiba, why aren't you biting the stranger?

326
00:14:38,320 --> 00:14:39,480
Your name is Shiba?

327
00:14:39,720 --> 00:14:41,120
You won't bite me, right?

328
00:14:44,360 --> 00:14:46,750
Since you helped Xiao Chi,

329
00:14:46,960 --> 00:14:48,440
next time you come to my tavern,

330
00:14:48,440 --> 00:14:49,360
I'll treat you to drinks.

331
00:14:49,360 --> 00:14:51,440
I never leave this mountain.

332
00:14:51,720 --> 00:14:53,380
Just bring the good wine here.

333
00:14:55,550 --> 00:14:57,410
There's only one jar of this wine.

334
00:14:58,120 --> 00:14:58,910
Why?

335
00:14:59,240 --> 00:15:00,440
This is Nverhong wine,

336
00:15:00,440 --> 00:15:01,720
brewed by her father

337
00:15:01,720 --> 00:15:03,270
when she was born.

338
00:15:03,270 --> 00:15:05,080
It was saved for her future husband.

339
00:15:05,080 --> 00:15:06,600
If you want to drink it,

340
00:15:06,600 --> 00:15:07,800
go talk to her father.

341
00:15:14,120 --> 00:15:15,150
Nver...

342
00:15:16,360 --> 00:15:17,150
Nverhong wine?

343
00:15:17,150 --> 00:15:17,840
Yes.

344
00:15:21,360 --> 00:15:22,120
Future...

345
00:15:23,510 --> 00:15:24,360
husband?

346
00:15:31,240 --> 00:15:32,840
When are we getting married?

347
00:15:33,120 --> 00:15:35,120
Who said I'm going to marry you?

348
00:15:35,120 --> 00:15:36,510
Good then.

349
00:15:46,550 --> 00:15:47,630
I have to admit,

350
00:15:47,630 --> 00:15:49,490
those two are quite well matched.

351
00:15:49,750 --> 00:15:50,910
Yes, they are.

352
00:15:51,440 --> 00:15:52,120
I guess

353
00:15:52,120 --> 00:15:53,030
Tang Zhaoxue

354
00:15:53,030 --> 00:15:54,080
will now put all her attention

355
00:15:54,080 --> 00:15:55,270
on Liu Xiyang.

356
00:15:56,120 --> 00:15:57,750
Then you'll have it easy.

357
00:15:58,440 --> 00:15:59,240
Yeah.

358
00:16:00,150 --> 00:16:02,680
But Mo's case still needs
to be investigated.

359
00:16:02,840 --> 00:16:04,720
I'll review the files
with Chengfeng later.

360
00:16:04,720 --> 00:16:06,360
I also have matters to attend to.

361
00:16:06,360 --> 00:16:07,490
Then let's split up.

362
00:16:08,360 --> 00:16:10,150
Be careful on your own.

363
00:16:10,750 --> 00:16:11,960
Don't worry.

364
00:16:11,960 --> 00:16:13,670
I'll be home before sunset.

365
00:16:30,750 --> 00:16:31,630
Jin Xi.

366
00:16:33,150 --> 00:16:35,120
We've been here for so many days.

367
00:16:35,840 --> 00:16:38,550
When will the marriage ceremony
actually take place?

368
00:16:38,550 --> 00:16:39,880
Don't worry, Princess.

369
00:16:40,120 --> 00:16:41,480
Lord Fei

370
00:16:41,480 --> 00:16:43,940
has already gone
to the palace to see Liu Chu.

371
00:16:45,120 --> 00:16:46,440
I'm not in a hurry.

372
00:16:47,080 --> 00:16:48,120
I just want to...

373
00:16:50,550 --> 00:16:51,960
You want to see Liu Chu?

374
00:16:53,960 --> 00:16:55,030
No, I don't.

375
00:16:55,360 --> 00:16:56,510
I just want to see

376
00:16:56,510 --> 00:16:57,970
whether he's worthy of me.

377
00:16:59,240 --> 00:17:00,000
Chengfeng.

378
00:17:00,440 --> 00:17:01,000
General.

379
00:17:02,480 --> 00:17:03,550
How is the princess?

380
00:17:03,550 --> 00:17:04,440
She hasn't skipped a meal—

381
00:17:04,440 --> 00:17:06,369
she's been eating well every time.

382
00:17:06,680 --> 00:17:07,510
Has anyone come in?

383
00:17:07,510 --> 00:17:08,349
No, General.

384
00:17:08,349 --> 00:17:09,480
We're watching closely—

385
00:17:09,480 --> 00:17:10,880
no fly could get through.

386
00:17:12,960 --> 00:17:13,829
Come with me.

387
00:17:14,000 --> 00:17:14,510
Yes.

388
00:17:15,349 --> 00:17:16,829
Keep a close eye on her.

389
00:17:17,160 --> 00:17:17,640
Yes.

390
00:17:24,069 --> 00:17:25,200
Is everything here?

391
00:17:25,920 --> 00:17:28,200
All case files from
the past twenty years in the capital

392
00:17:28,200 --> 00:17:28,960
are here.

393
00:17:29,960 --> 00:17:32,880
Then where are the Han family's files
from over ten years ago?

394
00:17:32,880 --> 00:17:34,510
I don't know.

395
00:17:34,510 --> 00:17:35,710
I just guard the door.

396
00:17:35,750 --> 00:17:37,030
I'm not even qualified to read them.

397
00:17:37,030 --> 00:17:38,750
Even if I were allowed to see them,

398
00:17:38,750 --> 00:17:39,750
I wouldn't understand them anyway.

399
00:17:39,750 --> 00:17:41,310
You don't need to know them.

400
00:17:42,110 --> 00:17:43,570
Just keep your mouth shut.

401
00:17:43,920 --> 00:17:44,920
Don't worry, Lieutenant Xu.

402
00:17:44,920 --> 00:17:46,350
I don't even talk in my sleep.

403
00:17:46,350 --> 00:17:47,160
You can leave.

404
00:17:47,680 --> 00:17:48,480
Okay.

405
00:17:51,480 --> 00:17:53,750
General, there are so many files here.

406
00:17:54,070 --> 00:17:55,640
How long will it take to find it?

407
00:17:55,640 --> 00:17:58,270
Aren't you full of energy after eating?

408
00:17:58,270 --> 00:18:00,670
Then search properly.
If you can't find it,

409
00:18:00,830 --> 00:18:01,640
you won't get to eat.

410
00:18:01,640 --> 00:18:02,480
Wait, this...

411
00:18:04,480 --> 00:18:06,350
Fine, I'll search. I don't believe

412
00:18:06,350 --> 00:18:07,810
I can't find a single file.

413
00:18:47,550 --> 00:18:48,810
Sir, I need some herbs.

414
00:18:52,310 --> 00:18:53,440
Two qian of Zhiyuan.

415
00:18:54,310 --> 00:18:55,110
Okay.

416
00:18:56,350 --> 00:18:57,810
Five qian of Xingnantian.

417
00:18:58,830 --> 00:18:59,640
Okay.

418
00:19:23,720 --> 00:19:24,510
Thank you.

419
00:20:04,510 --> 00:20:05,640
Well.

420
00:20:06,720 --> 00:20:08,160
It's my first time

421
00:20:08,680 --> 00:20:11,160
sneaking out of the palace at night.

422
00:20:12,510 --> 00:20:14,440
This is so exciting—it's fun.

423
00:20:16,160 --> 00:20:17,310
Chu.

424
00:20:17,720 --> 00:20:19,720
Do you still remember that courtyard?

425
00:20:19,720 --> 00:20:21,270
The one Xiao Chi is living in now—

426
00:20:21,270 --> 00:20:23,400
do you remember who used to live there?

427
00:20:23,680 --> 00:20:24,550
Of course I do.

428
00:20:25,110 --> 00:20:26,110
My sister.

429
00:20:27,480 --> 00:20:30,510
I remember I was the only one
who dared to come and go freely.

430
00:20:30,510 --> 00:20:31,720
Whenever I went there,

431
00:20:31,720 --> 00:20:35,120
my sister would always prepare
lots of delicious food for me.

432
00:20:35,960 --> 00:20:38,480
Ah… those were such happy days.

433
00:20:38,720 --> 00:20:40,450
Do you want to go and take a look?

434
00:20:43,750 --> 00:20:44,640
Let's go.

435
00:20:45,480 --> 00:20:46,010
Let's go.

436
00:20:46,720 --> 00:20:47,880
Hey, be careful.

437
00:20:49,240 --> 00:20:51,720
It's so late, and you're not sleeping.

438
00:20:51,720 --> 00:20:53,680
Dragging me out to sit in this courtyard—

439
00:20:53,680 --> 00:20:55,310
what exactly do you want?

440
00:20:58,350 --> 00:20:59,160
Princess.

441
00:20:59,830 --> 00:21:01,880
Tonight is the full moon—

442
00:21:01,920 --> 00:21:03,270
a very auspicious night.

443
00:21:03,270 --> 00:21:05,270
I've heard that any wish

444
00:21:05,270 --> 00:21:07,030
made tonight can come true.

445
00:21:07,640 --> 00:21:08,310
Really?

446
00:21:08,750 --> 00:21:09,720
Of course.

447
00:21:09,720 --> 00:21:11,250
When have I ever lied to you?

448
00:21:12,160 --> 00:21:13,030
Then I'll try it.

449
00:21:13,030 --> 00:21:13,510
Okay.

450
00:21:18,160 --> 00:21:19,350
May...

451
00:21:20,070 --> 00:21:23,160
May I and the Emperor
of Jinglan be married soon,

452
00:21:23,750 --> 00:21:25,610
and grow old together in harmony.

453
00:21:37,110 --> 00:21:37,920
Ouch!

454
00:21:46,920 --> 00:21:48,440
That hurts!

455
00:21:51,750 --> 00:21:52,750
Who are you?

456
00:21:54,030 --> 00:21:55,160
You don't know me?

457
00:21:56,240 --> 00:21:57,680
No, I don't.

458
00:21:57,880 --> 00:21:58,240
I...

459
00:22:01,070 --> 00:22:03,830
I'm General Xiao's elder brother.

460
00:22:04,200 --> 00:22:04,920
And you?

461
00:22:06,750 --> 00:22:07,920
I'm from Changmo.

462
00:22:08,030 --> 00:22:09,290
My name is Jiang Wanyu.

463
00:22:09,480 --> 00:22:11,270
You're the princess

464
00:22:11,270 --> 00:22:13,510
from Changmo who came
for the marriage alliance, right?

465
00:22:13,510 --> 00:22:14,350
Yeah.

466
00:22:17,440 --> 00:22:18,350
Well,

467
00:22:18,680 --> 00:22:20,750
why did you fall from up there?

468
00:22:24,880 --> 00:22:25,920
I...

469
00:22:27,680 --> 00:22:29,160
I was up there getting some fresh air.

470
00:22:29,160 --> 00:22:30,090
It's quite cool.

471
00:22:30,510 --> 00:22:31,370
What about you?

472
00:22:32,480 --> 00:22:35,610
My female official told me that
tonight is the full moon.

473
00:22:35,680 --> 00:22:38,070
If you drink wine
and make a wish to the moon,

474
00:22:38,070 --> 00:22:39,070
it will come true.

475
00:22:39,920 --> 00:22:42,480
What did you wish for?

476
00:22:42,480 --> 00:22:44,350
Your fall made me forget my wish.

477
00:22:48,350 --> 00:22:49,350
But,

478
00:22:50,310 --> 00:22:51,200
sir,

479
00:22:51,440 --> 00:22:52,960
that must've hurt, right?

480
00:22:53,440 --> 00:22:54,880
A sip of wine will ease the pain.

481
00:22:54,880 --> 00:22:56,080
I'll pass on the wine.

482
00:22:56,480 --> 00:22:57,000
I have things to do.

483
00:22:57,000 --> 00:22:58,060
I should get going.

484
00:22:58,480 --> 00:22:59,480
What's your name?

485
00:22:59,550 --> 00:23:00,350
Chu!

486
00:23:00,830 --> 00:23:01,760
Are you alright?

487
00:23:02,240 --> 00:23:03,030
Lord Fei.

488
00:23:04,960 --> 00:23:06,490
Princess, you are here too.

489
00:23:08,110 --> 00:23:08,720
Princess,

490
00:23:08,920 --> 00:23:10,000
allow me to introduce him.

491
00:23:10,000 --> 00:23:10,480
This is...

492
00:23:10,480 --> 00:23:11,160
Well,

493
00:23:11,160 --> 00:23:12,890
I'll tell you who I am next time.

494
00:23:13,350 --> 00:23:14,310
This is too awkward.

495
00:23:14,310 --> 00:23:15,350
Get me out of here.

496
00:23:16,480 --> 00:23:16,920
Chu.

497
00:23:17,920 --> 00:23:18,350
This...

498
00:23:18,350 --> 00:23:19,160
this way.

499
00:23:21,310 --> 00:23:23,110
Princess, we'll take our leave.

500
00:23:25,960 --> 00:23:27,620
This is Mo's medicinal pouch,

501
00:23:29,750 --> 00:23:31,480
Xiao Chi's hangover medicine,

502
00:23:32,310 --> 00:23:34,640
and the silver needles for his treatment.

503
00:23:41,920 --> 00:23:43,270
It's almost dawn.

504
00:23:43,440 --> 00:23:44,970
Why hasn't he come back yet?

505
00:25:09,790 --> 00:25:11,110
Why are you just getting back?

506
00:25:11,110 --> 00:25:12,240
I...

507
00:25:13,240 --> 00:25:14,840
I was busy all day yesterday.

508
00:25:16,350 --> 00:25:17,350
Go to sleep first.

509
00:25:17,510 --> 00:25:18,570
I'll head back now.

510
00:25:19,160 --> 00:25:19,720
Wait.

511
00:25:22,720 --> 00:25:24,270
I didn't treat you yesterday.

512
00:25:24,270 --> 00:25:26,440
The silver needles
have been prepared overnight.

513
00:25:26,440 --> 00:25:28,440
Now is the best time for acupuncture.

514
00:25:28,440 --> 00:25:29,270
Now?

515
00:25:29,590 --> 00:25:30,070
Yes.
